{"id": "xos045", "name": "Multi_File_X045", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Father! What happened!?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ER Doctor"], "content": "I don't know. Some people found him collapsed on side of the road covered in blood.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Gunshot wound......?</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ER Doctor"], "content": "I'm sorry, Miss Pauline. Your father has already lost too much blood. We need to do an emergency blood transfusion right away, but we don't have any AB type blood in our storage that matches his condition...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "My blood type is AB!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ER Doctor"], "content": "Really!? Are you willing to undergo a blood transfusion checkup...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Whatever! Let's get on it!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<i>*sob*... *sob*...</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The doctor said it's nothing major, it'll be alright.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Okay…\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ER Nurse"], "content": "Miss Pauline, you may visit your father now. You've got 10 minutes.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Thank you!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ER Nurse"], "content": "Sir, we're sorry. Only family members are allowed.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "He's the one who gave the blood!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry, it's okay. I'm still feeling a bit dizzy. I'll just rest here. Go on.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Okay!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[News]"], "content": "<i>...... Earlier today, a male agent who had sustained an injury was found lying here. By the time paramedics rushed to the scene, there were already no signs of life.</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[News]"], "content": "<i>By his side is a young girl who is in complete shock. She appears to have sustained no physical injuries, but her emotional state is very unstable. It's currently suspected that this girl may be the agent's daughter.</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[News]"], "content": "<i>The Administration Bureau is still in the process of clarifying the... Yes? Got it.\nNew information just came in. The agent who died in the line of duty was named Kyle Jackson. The girl by his side is his daughter, Shannon Jackson......</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Dad!? Shannon!?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Simon? Where did he go?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "I'm sorry, we're still unable to determine the reason behind your daughter's unique symptoms. She has suffered no brain damage, but her brain is just unable to disconnect with the virtual internet. She may need to remain in the hospital for a while so we can observe her symptoms.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "<i>*sob*... *sob*...</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "I'm very sorry about what happened to Mr. Jackson... he was a good agent.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Thank you. That's what everybody says...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Doctor.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Good morning.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Has there been any progress?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Yes, as for Shannon's condition, we've designated it \"Virtual-internet Related Post Traumatic Stress Disorder\", or \"VR PTSD\" for short. We suspect that the symptoms are residual effects of excessive emotional trauma clashing with the virtual Internet.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "I'm sorry. As of now, I can't allow you two to see her. Anything that can arouse her memory could potentially cause her to have an emotional breakdown. We're currently still doing our best to look for things she could come in contact with in her daily life that can evoke a normal reaction. The information you provided us has been a big help.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Have you discovered anything?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Yes. We've discovered that when she hears Simon's music, her emotions will be significantly more stabilized. She's able to maintain a stable emotional state even without the use of sedatives.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If possible, let me play for her in person. Maybe that can get more of a reaction out of her.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "No. Even if she so much as sees your faces, she will...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... So it's alright as long as I don't show my face?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "父さん！なんでこんな……っ！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["救急治療室 医者"], "content": "わかりません。\n発見された時には、血まみれで道端に倒れていたと……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">銃創……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["救急治療室 医者"], "content": "Paulineさん、お父様は出血が多く大変危険な状態です。\n輸血を必要としていますが、現在条件に合うAB型の血液の在庫がなく……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺がAB型です！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["救急治療室 医者"], "content": "本当ですか！？\nではまず検査を……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "そんな暇はない！早く！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うう……っ……ひっく……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "峠は越したって医者も言ってただろ。\n大丈夫だ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["救急治療室 看護師"], "content": "Paulineさん、お父様に面会されますか？\n10分間だけですが。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "はい！ありがとうございます！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["救急治療室 看護師"], "content": "申し訳ありません。\n面会はご家族の方だけとなっております。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "でも！輸血してくれたのは……！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry、いいんだ。\n俺はまだ少しフラフラする。\nここで待ってるから、行ってこい。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "わかった！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ニュース]"], "content": "<i>……先ほど、この場所に執法員の男性が倒れているのが発見されました。救急隊員が現場に到着した際には、すでに亡くなっており……</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ニュース]"], "content": "<i>また、すぐ隣には女の子がいたとのことです。女の子には外傷はありませんでしたが、精神的ショックを受けており、亡くなった執法員の娘の可能性が高いと見られています。</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ニュース]"], "content": "<i>管理局は現在も調査中で……はい？はい。わかりました。\nたった今、最新の情報が入って来ました。亡くなった執法員の名前はKyle Jacksonさん、隣で発見された女の子は、娘のShannon Jacksonちゃん……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "父さん！？Shannon！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon？どこに行ったの？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "申し訳ございません。\n娘さんの症状に関しては原因がわからない状況です。\n検査の結果、脳には損傷はありませんでしたが、神経ネットワークとの接続が切れない状態が続いています。\nしばらく入院していただいて、経過観察したほうがいいかもしれません。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "うう……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Jacksonさんの件についてですが……大変残念です。\n彼はとても素晴らしい執法員でした。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "ありがとうございます。\n皆さんにそう言っていただけて……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "先生。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "おはようございます。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "何か分かりましたか？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "はい、我々は現在Shannonちゃんの症状を「バーチャルインターネット心的外傷後ストレス障害」と呼んでいます。\n過度な心的ストレスと神経ネットワークの衝突により生まれた後遺症であると考えられます。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "申し訳ございません。\n今は面会を許可することができません。\nShannonちゃんの記憶を刺激してしまうと、彼女の負担になる可能性があるためです。\n現在、私たちの方でもShannonちゃんが日常生活で触れ合うものの中から、正常な反応を示すものを模索中です。\nご提供いただいた資料が大変役に立っています。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "何か分かりましたか？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "はい。\nShannonちゃんの情緒はSimonさんの曲を聴いている時、明らかな安定を見せ、鎮静剤も必要ないほどです。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "もし可能なら、自分で演奏して聴かせたいです。\nもしかしたら、何か反応があるかも……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "それはダメです。\nShannonちゃんは、Simonさんの顔を見てしまうと……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……顔を、出さなければいいんですね？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "爸！為什麼會這樣！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室醫生"], "content": "不知道，有人發現他全身是血倒在路邊……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">槍傷……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室醫生"], "content": "很抱歉，Pauline 小姐，令尊失血過多，急需輸血，但我們現在沒有符合條件的 AB 型血存貨……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我是 AB 型的！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室醫生"], "content": "真的嗎！？您願意做輸血用的條件檢測……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別廢話了！快點！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗚嗚……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "醫生都說沒有大礙了，沒事。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室護士"], "content": "Pauline 小姐，現在可以探望妳父親了，十分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室護士"], "content": "先生，抱歉，只許家人探望。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是他輸的血耶！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry，沒關係。我頭還有點暈，先在這邊休息一下。去吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新聞報導]"], "content": "<i>……稍早發現一名男性執法員在此負傷倒下，急救人員趕達時已經沒有生命跡象。</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新聞報導]"], "content": "<i>一旁還有一名倍受驚嚇的少女，看起來沒有物理的傷害，但精神狀況十分不穩定，疑似是該名執法員的女兒。</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新聞報導]"], "content": "<i>管理局目前還在釐清……是？是。\n剛剛傳來最新的消息，殉職執法員的名字為 Kyle Jackson，一旁的則是她的女兒 Shannon Jackson……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "爸！？Shannon！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon？跑哪去了？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，妳女兒的症狀，我們還是查不出原因。她的腦部也完全沒有任何損傷，但是與精神網路的連結卻無法中斷。也許還需要留院觀察一段時間。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Jackson 先生的事情，我很遺憾……他是位好執法員。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "謝謝，大家都這麼說……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "醫生。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "兩位早安。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有新的結果嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，Shannon 的症狀，我們現在命名為「精神網路相關電子創傷症候群」。懷疑是過度的精神創傷與精神網路產生衝突留下的後遺症。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，目前還沒辦法讓兩位探望她。任何能勾起她回憶的事物都有可能導致她的情緒崩潰。我們目前還在從她日常生活中能接觸到的事物中盡量找出能讓她有正常反應的東西，你們提供的資料很有用。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有什麼發現嗎？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，我們目前發現她在聽到 Simon 的音樂時情緒會明顯安定許多，不需要鎮定劑也能維持一個穩定的精神狀態。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果可以的話，讓我親自演奏給她聽，也許她會有點反應。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "不，她只要看見你們的臉，還是會……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……不露臉就行了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아빠! 대체 무슨 일이야!?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["응급실 의사"], "content": "모르겠습니다. 피투성이가 되어 쓰러져 있던 걸 누군가 발견했습니다.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">총상......? </font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["응급실 의사"], "content": "죄송합니다, Pauline 씨. 출혈이 너무 심해서 당장 수혈을 해야만 하는데... 현재 아버님의 조건에 부합하는 AB형 혈액이 없는 상황이라...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "제가 AB형입니다!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["응급실 의사"], "content": "정말입니까! ? 그렇다면 수혈용으로 적합한지 테스트를 해야 하는데...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아 됐고 빨리해주세요!!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "흐흑......흑......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "의사 선생님이 큰 문제는 없을 거래.\n그러니까 괜찮을 거야\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["응급실 간호사"], "content": "Pauline 씨, 지금 아버님 면회 가능해요. 10분 동안.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "감사합니다!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["응급실 간호사"], "content": "선생님? 죄송합니다. \n면회는 가족 관계에 있는 사람만 가능합니다.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "그래도 쟤가 수혈해준 사람인데!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry, 괜찮아.\n머리가 조금 어지러운 것 같네. 난 여기서 좀 쉬고 있을 테니, 넌 빨리 가봐.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응, 알았어!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[뉴스]"], "content": "<i>조금 전 이 자리에서 집법원 남성이 쓰러져 있는 것이 발견되었습니다. 구급 대원이 현장에 도착했을 때에는 이미 숨져있었고......</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......? \n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[뉴스]"], "content": "<i>또, 바로 옆에 있던 여자아이는 외상은 없었지만 정신적 충격을 받은 듯 보이며 목숨을 잃은 집법원의 딸일 것으로 추측하고 있습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[뉴스]"], "content": "<i>관리국은 현재도 조사 중에 있으며......네? 네, 알겠습니다.\n지금 막 속보가 들어왔습니다. 사망한 집법원의 이름은 Kyle Jackson 씨, 옆에서 발견된 여자아이는 사망한 집법원의 딸 Shannon Jackson 양이라고......</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아...아버지!? Shannon!? \n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......Simon? 어딜 급하게 뛰어가는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "죄송합니다.\n따님의 증상에 관해서는 원인을 알 수 없는 상황입니다.\n검사 결과 뇌에는 손상이 없었지만 정신 네트워크와의 접속이 끊기지 않는 상태가 지속되고 있습니다.\n입원시켜서 잠깐 동안은 경과를 지켜보는 것이 좋을 것 같습니다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "흑흑......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Jackson 씨의 일은 참으로 유감입니다....\n그 사람은 참 좋은 집법원이었어요.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "감사합니다.\n모두들 그렇게 말씀해주셔서....\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "의사 선생님?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "오셨군요, 두 분.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "새로운 결과는 있었나요?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "네, 우리는 현재 Shannon 씨의 증상을 [가상 네트워크 외상 후 스트레스 장애]라고 부르고 있습니다.\n과도한 심적 스트레스와 정신 네트워크의 충돌로 인해 생겨난 후유증이라고 볼 수 있죠.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "죄송합니다.\n지금은 면회를 허가할 수 없습니다.\nShannon의 기억을 자극해 버리면 정신 상태에 부담이 갈 수도 있어요.\n현재 우리도 Shannon 씨가 일상생활에서 만나는 것들 중 정상적인 반응을 나타내는 것들을 찾고 있는 중입니다.\n제공해주신 자료가 큰 도움이 되고 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "뭔가 발견한 것이라도?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "네.\nShannon의 감정은 Simon 씨의 곡을 듣고 있을 때 분명 안정을 보이고 있어요. 진정제도 필요 없을 정도입니다.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "만약 가능하다면, 제가 직접 연주해서 들려주고 싶어요.\n어쩌면 뭔가 반응이 있을지도......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "그건 안 됩니다. 만약 여러분의 얼굴을 보기라도 한다면 발작이 시작될 수도...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......얼굴을 가리면요?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "爸！為什麼會這樣！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急診室醫生"], "content": "不知道，有人發現他全身是血倒在路邊……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">槍傷……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation"