 "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon？跑哪去了？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，妳女兒的症狀，我們還是查不出原因。她的腦部也完全沒有任何損傷，但是與精神網路的連結卻無法中斷。也許還需要留院觀察一段時間。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Jackson 先生的事情，我很遺憾……他是位好執法員。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "謝謝，大家都這麼說……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "醫生。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "兩位早安。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有新的結果嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，Shannon 的症狀，我們現在命名為「精神網路相關電子創傷症候群」。懷疑是過度的精神創傷與精神網路產生衝突留下的後遺症。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，目前還沒辦法讓兩位探望她。任何能勾起她回憶的事物都有可能導致她的情緒崩潰。我們目前還在從她日常生活中能接觸到的事物中盡量找出能讓她有正常反應的東西，你們提供的資料很有用。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有什麼發現嗎？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，我們目前發現她在聽到 Simon 的音樂時情緒會明顯安定許多，不需要鎮定劑也能維持一個穩定的精神狀態。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果可以的話，讓我親自演奏給她聽，也許她會有點反應。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "不，她只要看見你們的臉，還是會……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……不露臉就行了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "爸！为什么会这样！ ？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急诊室医生"], "content": "不知道，有人发现他全身是血倒在路边……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">枪伤……？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急诊室医生"], "content": "很抱歉，Pauline 小姐，令尊失血过多，急需输血，但我们现在没有符合条件的 AB 型血存货……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我是 AB 型的！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急诊室医生"], "content": "真的吗！ ？您愿意做输血用的条件检测……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "别废话了！快点！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "呜呜……呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "医生都说没有大碍了，没事。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急诊室护士"], "content": "Pauline 小姐，现在可以探望妳父亲了，十分钟。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "谢谢！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["急诊室护士"], "content": "先生，抱歉，只许家人探望。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是他输的血耶！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry，没关系。我头还有点晕，先在这边休息一下。去吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新闻报导]"], "content": "<i>……稍早发现一名男性执法员在此负伤倒下，急救人员赶达时已经没有生命迹象。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新闻报导]"], "content": "<i>一旁还有一名倍受惊吓的少女，看起来没有物理的伤害，但精神状况十分不稳定，疑似是该名执法员的女儿。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！ ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[新闻报导]"], "content": "<i>管理局目前还在厘清……是？是。\n刚刚传来最新的消息，殉职执法员的名字为 Kyle Jackson，一旁的则是她的女儿 Shannon Jackson……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "爸！ ？ Shannon！ ？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon？跑哪去了？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_05_17]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，妳女儿的症状，我们还是查不出原因。她的脑部也完全没有任何损伤，但是与精神网路的连结却无法中断。也许还需要留院观察一段时间。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "Jackson 先生的事情，我很遗憾……他是位好执法员。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "谢谢，大家都这么说……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Hospital01_696_09_15]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "医生。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "两位早安。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有新的结果吗？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，Shannon 的症状，我们现在命名为「精神网路相关电子创伤症候群」。怀疑是过度的精神创伤与精神网路产生冲突留下的后遗症。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "很抱歉，目前还没办法让两位探望她。任何能勾起她回忆的事物都有可能导致她的情绪崩溃。我们目前还在从她日常生活中能接触到的事物中尽量找出能让她有正常反应的东西，你们提供的资料很有用。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有什么发现吗？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "是，我们目前发现她在听到 Simon 的音乐时情绪会明显安定许多，不需要镇定剂也能维持一个稳定的精神状态。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果可以的话，让我亲自演奏给她听，也许她会有点反应。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Jacob"], "content": "不，她只要看见你们的脸，还是会……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……不露脸就行了吗？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}